testsuite.system-out: === There are subway routes: Red Line, Mattapan Trolley, Orange Line, Green Line B, Green Line C, Green Line D, Green Line E, Blue Line === === The subway route with the most stops is Green-B with 24 stops. === === The subway route with the fewest stops is Mattapan with 8 stops. === === These stops connect two or more subway routes: {North Station=[Green-C, Green-E, Orange], Government Center=[Blue, Green-C, Green-E], Haymarket=[Green-C, Green-E, Orange], Hynes Convention Center=[Green-C, Green-B, Green-D], Boylston=[Green-C, Green-B, Green-E, Green-D], State=[Blue, Orange], Kenmore=[Green-C, Green-B, Green-D], Copley=[Green-C, Green-B, Green-E, Green-D], Downtown Crossing=[Red, Orange], Park Street=[Red, Green-C, Green-B, Green-E, Green-D], Arlington=[Green-C, Green-B, Green-E, Green-D]} === === You need to travel the [Green-C, Green-E] line to get from North Station to Arlington. ===
